sociodemographicDescripton: Complete the fields below, pay attention to the data you enter as this will allow evaluators to find your process more effectively. The Organizational Competencies Test is an evaluation instrument that will identify some of your most predominant behaviors in work contexts. It will last approximately 15 minutes. Answer honestly and paying attention to each of the questions, many successes.

autoDescriptionText: Reflect on the aspects that you consider outstanding in yourself or that others have highlighted at some point. You can also include information about areas where you think you need to improve or continue to strengthen. Write at least four lines to give us a better understanding about you
